query:
SELECT 
  dr.id,
  dr.date,
  dr.branchId,
  b.name as branchName,
  dr.cashRevenue,
  dr.networkRevenue,
  dr.madaRevenue,
  dr.totalRevenue,
  dr.isMatching
FROM daily_revenues dr
LEFT JOIN branches b ON dr.branchId = b.id
WHERE dr.branchId = (SELECT id FROM branches WHERE name LIKE '%طويق%' LIMIT 1)
  AND dr.date >= '2026-01-15'
  AND dr.date <= '2026-01-21'
ORDER BY dr.date ASC;
